bug.short_desc: OpenGLRaw fails to build on armv7hl: "fork: resource exhausted"
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
I am not sure why but building OpenGLRaw (part of haskell-platform) fails randomly and very frequently on armv7hl. It build initially with ghc-7.10.3 but maybe this was just luck.
